title: MNAs Mubarak Zeb, Aurangzeb Khichi call on PM Shehbaz Sharif
content:
ISLAMABAD, Nov 4 (APP): Members of National Assembly Mubarak Zeb and Aurangzeb Khichi separately called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Monday at the Parliament House.
During the meetings, both the members expressed their trust on the government policies.
They also reaffirmed their commitment to continue supporting the government.
Minister for Economic Affairs Ahad Khan Cheema and Minister for Information and Broadcasting Attaullah Tarar were present in the meetings.
